examples.en: The paint is peeling away already.
The paint in my house is peeling off.
The paper was peeling from the wall.
She got sunburned and her back is peeling.
examples.ru: Она обгорела на солнце, и у неё шелушится спина.

examples.en: The paint was peeling on the window frames.
Marie stood at the sink, peeling potatoes (=cutting off the skin).
examples.ru: Мари стояла у раковины и чистила картошку (т.е. срезала с неё кожицу).
